                                {
                                    Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                    Operation: "EQUALS",
                                    Name: "no_defeated_arcade_challenger_1"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "fight_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Ask for the house odds",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    Cmd: "title @initiator actionbar [{\"text\":\"House odds, freshly calculated this morning: yes.\"}]"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "odds_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "Not this spin",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "New face on the floor. The League seat you took at the top bought you a chair here - the Arcade always seats a Champion. The house always spins."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Everyone told the Company to shut this wing down for a fast-cash floor. Nobody did. So the wheel still turns, and every turn is a wager - it can flatten the levels, flip the table to doubles, or fatten the purse. The wheel decides, not you."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Fast teams, glass jaws, no second chances - my kind of game. House rules: the wheel spins once per fight, and no fight starts without a stake on the table. Spin first, then sit."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "(he taps the table twice before speaking) Not superstition. Risk management. I have a system - six systems, technically. They take turns failing."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The wheel lands doubles more often when the floor is freshly swept. I keep records. Suki calls my records one napkin. It is a very thorough napkin."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Gambler Fritz",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
